exceptions.exn: Cannot coerce RR to an evaluable reference.

In environment W : Type A1 : Type B1 : Type A : Type B : Type L : Type A2 : Type B2 : Type RR : rel A1 B1 -> A -> B -> Prop R1 : klr W A1 B1 w : W x : A y : B X : Prop -> rel B B -> B -> B -> Prop k0 : (rel A1 B1 -> rel A B) -> klr W A1 B1 -> klr W A B acc0 : L -> rel W W H1 : RR (R1 w) x y Unable to unify "RR (R1 w) x y" with "k0 RR R1 w x y".

original: intros. unfold RIntro, k1, RR, R1. simpl. intros H1. apply H1.
